28:07.235 --> 28:12.244
if I might have had an
entirely different life

28:12.245 --> 28:15.084
with a different man.

28:17.589 --> 28:20.595
Did you ask me a question
in that letter, Billy?

28:26.273 --> 28:28.277
I did.

28:32.719 --> 28:36.727
I would've said yes.

28:57.803 --> 28:59.005
Need a hand?

28:59.006 --> 29:01.175
Oh, uh, do you mind?

29:01.176 --> 29:02.544
Not at all.

29:02.545 --> 29:04.582
Glad for the distraction.

29:04.583 --> 29:06.686
Just waiting for my wife.

29:06.687 --> 29:10.227
Oh. Have a nice stay?

29:10.228 --> 29:13.566
No, we didn't, uh...

29:13.567 --> 29:15.370
yeah, she-she doesn't know I'm here.

29:17.242 --> 29:19.712
I taught her how to drive,
but, uh, she never really got

29:19.713 --> 29:22.618
