29:51.845 --> 29:54.048
No, he's more than that.

29:54.049 --> 29:55.384
If she were here, she'd
probably tell you

29:55.385 --> 29:58.156
he's the love of her life.

29:58.157 --> 30:00.494
Hell, I thought we were happy, you know?

30:00.495 --> 30:01.629
