30:33.862 --> 30:35.063
You should.

30:35.064 --> 30:37.402
I would, if I were you.

30:43.280 --> 30:46.452
I wish you would say something.

30:46.453 --> 30:48.457
It would be better
than all this silence.

30:51.797 --> 30:53.299
Just tell me what you're thinking.

30:53.300 --> 30:54.302
Ooh.

30:56.140 --> 30:57.674
All right, you want to
know what I'm thinking?

30:57.675 --> 30:59.178
- Yeah.
