you spent half the meal

31:07.262 --> 31:08.898
talking about the ways that the clinic,

31:08.899 --> 31:10.033
where you are a trusted employee,

31:10.034 --> 31:11.569
could be managed better.

31:11.570 --> 31:13.908
It's... I-I don't know
what the word for it is.

31:13.909 --> 31:17.781
Uh, indecent, maybe? Shameful?

31:17.782 --> 31:19.585
Wh...

31:19.586 --> 31:23.459
